               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝnä Māryām ba-wǝsṭä hagärä Bartos “Prayer of Our Lady
                     Mary in the Country of Bartos” (fols. 4ra-39ra)
 II) Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝnä
                     Māryām ba-Dabra Golgota, Prayer of Our Lady Mary on Mount Golgotha on the 21st
                     of Sane (fols. 39rb-63rb)
 III) Nǝgǝränni sǝmäkä … “Tell me your name …”
                     (fols. 63rb-67rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
