                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Fine</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (vivid red).</seg>The scribe is probably the same
                        as the one of Ms. NSM-016.<date>19th century.</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ሰላ</abbr> for <expan>ሰላም </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#7rb">7rb</locus>, 9rb, 28vb)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>አ/አም፡ ኦወ፡ ወፍ፡</abbr> for <expan>አምህለከ፡ ኦወልድየ፡ ወፍቁርየ፡ </expan>
                              (e.g., <locus target="#42rb">42rb</locus>, 42vb, 43ra)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>መ/መሐ</abbr> for <expan>መሐልኩ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#58vb">58vb</locus>, 59ra, 60rb)</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the donor; a few lines on the
                           incipit page of Text I and II, alternating with black lines; the word
                           salām (e.g., fols. 7ra, 8ra, 28ra); elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#4r">4r</locus> (incipit page of text I): simple coloured
                        (red, black and light amber) ornamental band; interlaces.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#67va">f. 67va</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#67va">67va</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ የማርያም፡ ገናህት፡ ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡
                              ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በስልጣነ … </quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#67va">67va</locus>: This book is of Māryām Gänaht, may
                              the one who stole it and erased it, be excommunicated by the authority
                              of … </quote>
                           <note> In Gǝʿǝz and Amharic. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Interlinear corrections: fols, 13vb, 15va.
 - Spaces
                           for rubrication left unfilled: <locus target="#11ra">11ra</locus>, 16va,
                           19va, 28rb.
 - Writing exercises: <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 2r,
                           3r, 44v.
 - Drawing exercise on the inner face of the right
                           board.
 - ff. 1-2 are unruled.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
