               <provenance>The name Gabra Masqal is mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas throughout the Ms. Besides, the names of his father and
                     his mother, Gabra Māryām and Walatta Śǝllāse, are mentioned in the explicit of
                     Text III.</provenance></history>
